  <brief_title>Ultrasound-Assisted Lumbar Puncture in Children</brief_title>
  <official_title>Emergency Physician Performed Ultrasound-Assisted Lumbar Puncture in a Pediatric Population: A Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
